WEBVTT

00:00:21.330 --> 00:00:23.369
{whispering] She's gonna wake
up and she's gonna see us here.

00:00:23.460 --> 00:00:24.531
{whispering] It's not fair.

00:00:26.459 --> 00:00:27.529
How did she get in here?

00:00:27.753 --> 00:00:29.632
She comes in when she has nightmares.

00:00:30.755 --> 00:00:32.711
How often does she have nightmares?

00:00:36.926 --> 00:00:37.917
Don't start.

00:00:37.969 --> 00:00:39.962
You don't know what it's like
to raise a child alone.

